{"tid":48754,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：唔好寄太大期望","createTime":"2016-12-21T09:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T16:23:19.000Z","uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13d55de5f27934cc3b74b5ecbb2ddf1d7deac9bf","tid":48754,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"又到《三點九沈大師》時間，個市今日反彈返百零點，都係去到21900之前有阻力，睇返個動力就唔係太強，只係喘定返，我覺得如果想博反彈都要小心一啲，指數向上空間未必會太多，個別個股可能超跌有一定反彈幅度，但都係個別o黎睇啦。<br />\n<br />\n暫時我會睇澳門賭業係比較上強勢啲，另外騰訊（<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=syxOsB47fWTGQPYUHE82sgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=88e843bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>）都有少少反彈力度，純粹搵一隻半隻博下好啦，唔好寄太大期望，因為始終個市成交細，比較淡靜。"},{"pid":"cd5014169a50e38a65140bc3c46c8940611c4e59","tid":48754,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沈大師"},{"pid":"ba3d04e95d610e227b3a94abaa82ca403a0b1b68","tid":48754,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"已經冬至，大師仲未出2017年香港經濟運程預測？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4102050e51c1386391204ec8f4a8ecb059115c7","tid":48754,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"賭股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae1a66ed018ae09429dcbe5c1af2510e2e73c2c","tid":48754,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n700都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521cb5c3d71d2777fc76bbf21bb20955a8d17085","tid":48754,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"老實講，我覺得大師幾準&hellip;<br />\n但我知道&he